snippet.title: MICRO MURDER: But It's Robots So It's OK
snippet.description:
A short game of MM:BIRSIO, getting my ass kicked by the AI. But it's ok because it's robots.

Play the game online: https://tictactoad.itch.io/micro-murder

MICRO MURDER: But It's Robots So It's OK is a game by Tic Tac Toad. The game is an artillery game (or, a Worms clone) for your PICO-8. Play against your friends or the AI!
